            <h2>Ingredients</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Bread of choice - pita bread, ciabatta, etc.</li>
                <li>Green base - arugula is my fave</li>
                <li>Pickled element - pickles, sauerkraut, pickled red onion, etc.</li>
                <li>Fun veggies - radishes, peppers, pepperoncinis, etc.</li>
                <li>Tangy element - sun dried tomatoes</li>
                <li>Tofu feta</li>
                <li>Protein - veggie dogs, tofurkey/ham, tempeh, etc.</li>
                <li>Salt, pepper, and herbs to taste</li>
                <li>Sauce - pesto, hummus, cream cheese, or aioli</li>
                
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Instructions</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Chop all ingredients up and stuff into a pita wrap or bread!</li>
              
            </ol>
